      "description": "Repository quality pass — no user-facing behavior change.\n\n- **Dependencies:** removed `@javalent/utilities` by reimplementing the icon search on Obsidian's native `AbstractInputSuggest`, eliminating the transitive Svelte dependency. `npm audit` now reports **0 vulnerabilities**.\n- **Linting:** enabled type-aware `typescript-eslint` rules and fixed the violations; `npm run lint` is clean.\n- **License:** added a canonical `LICENSE` file so it's detected automatically (MIT, unchanged).",
